          Suburbs of Lahore — Lahore's Largest Housing Project in Lahore West
        </p>
        <p class="project-desc">A gated community featuring Cinema, Pizza Hut, Gloria Jeans, Jade Cafe, Water Filtration Plant, 24/7 Power Backup, Underground Electricity, Jamia Masjid, Sports Complex, Steppingstone School, and Al-Jalil Healthcare. A complete ecosystem for modern, secure, and luxurious living.</p>
        <div class="project-plots">
          <a href="#contact" class="plot-card">
            <div class="plot-card-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?w=400&q=70')"></div>
            <div class="plot-card-overlay"></div>
            <div class="plot-card-body">
              <span class="plot-card-badge">Available</span>
              <div class="plot-card-main">
                <span class="plot-card-num">3</span>
                <span class="plot-card-unit">Marla</span>
              </div>
              <span class="plot-card-cta">Inquire →</span>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="#contact" class="plot-card">
            <div class="plot-card-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570129477492-45c003edd2be?w=400&q=70')"></div>
            <div class="plot-card-overlay"></div>
            <div class="plot-card-body">
              <span class="plot-card-badge">Available</span>
              <div class="plot-card-main">
                <span class="plot-card-num">5</span>
                <span class="plot-card-unit">Marla</span>
              </div>
              <span class="plot-card-cta">Inquire →</span>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="#contact" class="plot-card">
